RedTree Systems Framework - http://framework.redtreesystems.com

The latest version currently resides at
  git://github.com/jcorbinredtree/framework.git


Basic site layout:
  site_document_root/
    SITE/
      framework/ -- this repository
      local/     -- site specific components, modules, themes, etc
      writable/  -- contains resources writable by the webserver


Example site initialization:
  % mkdir site && cd site
  % git init
  % mkdir -p SITE/{local,writable}
  % echo 'cache/*' > SITE/writable/.gitignore
  % git add SITE/writable
  % git submodule add git://github.com/jcorbinredtree/framework.git SITE/framework
  % cp SITE/framework/index.php .
  % git add index.php
  % git commit -m 'Initial commit'
